sentences.pinyin: Zhège shān gāo yú nàgè shān.
sentences.translation: This mountain is higher than that mountain.

sentences.simplifiedText: 他的成绩高于班级平均水平，被选为年级优秀生。
sentences.traditionalText: 他的成績高於班級平均水平，被選為年級優秀生。
sentences.pinyin: Tā de chéngjì gāo yú bānjí píngjūn shuǐpíng, bèi xuǎn wèi niánjí yōuxiù shēng.
sentences.translation: His grades are higher than the class average, so he was selected as an outstanding student of the grade.
